     {q:"Machine learning allows computer systems to ___.", options:["Remain completely unchanged regardless of new information","Replace the need for any programming","Function with no connection to data at all","Improve their performance through exposure to data"], answer:3},
     {q:"Which is an example of a real-world application of artificial intelligence?", options:["An object unrelated to any form of intelligence","A device that cannot process any information","A tool with no connection to computing technology","A virtual assistant that responds to voice commands"], answer:3},
     {q:"Why might machine learning models require large amounts of data?", options:["Machine learning models never require any data","Data has no connection to how machine learning models function","Large amounts of data always make a model less accurate","More data can help the model identify patterns and improve accuracy"], answer:3},
     {q:"Why is understanding artificial intelligence increasingly important today?", options:["Artificial intelligence has no real-world relevance","AI is used exclusively in fictional stories","This technology has no connection to modern life","AI technology is being used across many industries and everyday applications"], answer:3}
